Name: Choi
About the game: Choi, who is on the verge of dying from boredom, is visited by a demon one day. The demon suggests Choi to try him space-time travel. Choi accepts the offer and travels through time and space. The Space Police, who protects the order of the universe, discovers that time and space are being distorted by Choi and begins to chase Choi. Choi, your alter ego! Don't get caught by the space police and start traveling through time and space! This version is the first version of space-time travel. In the future version, various space-time travel will be introduced. In order to successfully travel, develop the ability to avoid being caught by the space police through this version. Feature Run away to Telebox with information of distance to the Telebox Hide behind obstacles to avoid the Space Police Eat burgers to recover stamina lost from running and to level up in order to transform into more strong and agile Choi Annoy the Space Police by kicking obstacles to Space police You can do Walk, Run, Kick, Somersault in this version
